      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "PSALM 98:1-9\nMIZMOR.\nShiru l'Adonai shir chadash,\nki niflaot asah,\nhoshiah lo y'mino uz'ro-a kodsho.\nHodia Adonai y'shuato,\nl'einei hagoyim gilah tzidkato.\nZachar chasdo ve-emunato\nI'veit Yisrael, ra-u chol afsei aret\net y'shuat Eloheinu.\nHariu l'Adonai kol haaretz\npitz'chu v'ran'nu v'zameiru.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-14T17:46:36.037Z",
