          "value": "xywh=pixel:1477.7894736842102,4481.0526315789475,2512.6315789473692,1678.9473684210534"
        }
      },
      "@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "A PSALM.\nSing to Adonai a new song,\nfor God has worked wonders;\nGod's right hand, God's holy arm,\nhas won God victory.\nAdonai has manifested God's victory,\nhas displayed God's triumph in the sight of the nations.\nGod was mindful of God's steadfast love and faithfulness\ntoward the house of Israel;\nall the ends of the earth beheld the victory of our God.\nRaise a shout to Adonai, all the earth,\nbreak into joyous songs of praise!",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
